            'Where Ravana meditated to please Lord Shiva and the Pandavas found refuge during their exile, as mentioned in the Mahabharata.'}
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Religious Importance -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
