          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700">
            Near Adi Kailash lies Om Parvat, where nature has carved the sacred Om (‡•ê) symbol in snow, visible throughout the year - a divine miracle.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Pilgrims Choose Adi Kailash -->
